
To install CloudI, do the following steps:

0) ./autogen.sh

1) ./configure (--prefix=/path/to/installation/directory)

2) make

3) make install

The installation includes the various tests along with the default configuration
to start the tests.


Within the installation directory the "bin/cloudi" script controls CloudI.

To start CloudI:
bin/cloudi start

To stop CloudI:
bin/cloudi stop

